{"tid":1534642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人問美國討論緊既《香港人權與民主法案》係乜，同埋點解環支持⋯","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:00:14.000Z","uid":14503,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6b611bc1a7675f5489fe1e54b8f15c14c8af27d2","tid":1534642,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"首先《香港人權與民主法案》唔係之前提個條香港關係法⋯<br />\n<br />\nQuoted from wiki:<br />\n<br />\n香港人權與民主法案（Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act）是美國討論中之法案，由美國國會及行政當局中國委員會主席眾議員基斯&middot;史密斯、聯席主席參議員馬可&middot;魯比奧和參議員湯&middot;卡頓共同提出。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目的是美方對涉及鎮壓基本自由的香港或中國大陸的政府官員，設立懲罰機制，包括禁止涉事官員入境美國及凍結其在美國之資產。</strong></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ba3a793fa4be9c8a3583e5af703f42e0e79c7566","tid":1534642,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96d01717fe74dffec1fdacac8d6b9487190d06cb","tid":1534642,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔入美國境又無美國資產呢?"},{"pid":"ddbdde9e4daf48fde1126c1afa5c93eb04188f6e","tid":1534642,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96d01717fe74dffec1fdacac8d6b9487190d06cb","tid":1534642,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔入美國境又無美國資產呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141478b1451f4f877a0713de0e31eb1d39ea75bf","tid":1534642,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96d01717fe74dffec1fdacac8d6b9487190d06cb","tid":1534642,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔入美國境又無美國資產呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"好似話與美國有業務關係既機構都要遵守"},{"pid":"8b6ef70720c6d5db04e5cb8354979cd80f757166","tid":1534642,"uid":14503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"96d01717fe74dffec1fdacac8d6b9487190d06cb","tid":1534642,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔入美國境又無美國資產呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:26:34.000Z","msg":"一世用人民幣"},{"pid":"e99e2c58331876d26f20fc8ad5ae8ca571e212ac","tid":1534642,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"141478b1451f4f877a0713de0e31eb1d39ea75bf","tid":1534642,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96d01717fe74dffec1fdacac8d6b9487190d06cb","tid":1534642,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔入美國境又無美國資產呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"好似話與美國有業務關係既機構都要遵守"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"假設我去極都係日本 韓國 馬拉 台灣咁計 資產係晒中國同香港<br />\n咁樣有冇實質影響